\section{Test Cases}
\label{sec:test-cases}

In this exercise we are to define in ML the following functions:
\begin{align}
  plus x y &= x + y\\
  times \;x\;y &= x \times y\\
  plus \;x\;y &= x + y\\
  times \;x\;y &= x \times y
\end{align}

